invoicesById.description: Invoices allow you to bill a Client for your products and/or services, and help you keep track of your income in FreshBooks

amount.description: Total invoice amount, taxes inc. (Read Only)

amount_outstanding.description: Outstanding amount on invoice from partial payment, etc. (Read Only)
